  "detailed_description": "<h1>Local co-op</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/869bc40851500e0d7062194b049edceb.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><i>It came from space and ate our brains</i> is a local co-op game for up to four players. However, with <strong>Steam Remote Play Together</strong> you can play with other people online!<br><br>You can also switch back to the <strong>classic version of the game</strong>, which supports online co-op.</p><br><h1>Steam Remote Play Together</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/d53b2979f565d6b60da0811ed2213ad5.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=211 /></span><br>Steam Remote Play Together is a brand new feature allowing people to play together online. <br><br><strong>How do I use Steam Remote Play Together?</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Launch ‘It came from space and ate our brains’<br></li><li>Open your Friends List and right-click to Invite your friends.<br></li><li>They accept the invite in the chat window and... That’s it!</li></ul><br>To access your Friends List, you may need to open Steam Overlay (Shift+Tab by default).</p><br><h1>Classic version</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/b0fef969c407bd14fc5eac0ed2e5531e.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br>You can play the classic version of the game (online mode included) by switching to another branch on Steam:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Right-click on the game in the Steam Library<br></li><li>Select Properties<br></li><li>Head to the BETAS tab<br></li><li>Choose <i>classic - Original version of the game</i></li></ul></p><br><h1>Chat with us on Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/53599114bb5c3a05a5afe4c0e8cc4d48.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><i>It came from space and ate our brains</i> is a unique <strong>arcade top-down shooter</strong>. Looking for addicting gameplay elements, <strong>four-player local co-op</strong> mode, and tons of aliens to send into oblivion? Yes, yes and yes? You’re in the right place!<br><br>A merciless alien species has invaded the Earth and they feed on human brains (duh). Wander atmospheric locations as a no-nonsense kind of guy with the two essentials in life—a flashlight and something to turn aliens into goo. Things look pretty bad and there’s chaos everywhere! Time to save the world! Again!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/[BRA]_STEAM_gif_Alien_slayer3_616x206-px.gif?t=1654861170\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/44d85410fa9e0dfba57e1276d0b458ca.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=102 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/0be1b23d199d4160b34f42e83bfa65cd.poster.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/0be1b23d199d4160b34f42e83bfa65cd.webm?t=1654861170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/0be1b23d199d4160b34f42e83bfa65cd.mp4?t=1654861170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/[BRA]_STEAM_gif_Local_co-op_616x206-px.gif?t=1654861170\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/e2ab38130683f217ba1dfb2238c2e45b.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br>Enjoy new features and a major visual overhaul as you boost your high score even higher. Become a pro in no time with a brand new prologue to the game. The re-balanced difficulty makes shooting aliens even more fun for both new and experienced players.<br><br>Can you make it through endless hordes of brain-eating aliens? We mean, like, with your brain intact and everything. Prove it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/e866f28cb2b8bd47d55b69764b3bd525.poster.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/e866f28cb2b8bd47d55b69764b3bd525.webm?t=1654861170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/e866f28cb2b8bd47d55b69764b3bd525.mp4?t=1654861170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/53599114bb5c3a05a5afe4c0e8cc4d48.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><i>It came from space and ate our brains</i> is a unique <strong>arcade top-down shooter</strong>. Looking for addicting gameplay elements, <strong>four-player local co-op</strong> mode, and tons of aliens to send into oblivion? Yes, yes and yes? You’re in the right place!<br><br>A merciless alien species has invaded the Earth and they feed on human brains (duh). Wander atmospheric locations as a no-nonsense kind of guy with the two essentials in life—a flashlight and something to turn aliens into goo. Things look pretty bad and there’s chaos everywhere! Time to save the world! Again!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/[BRA]_STEAM_gif_Alien_slayer3_616x206-px.gif?t=1654861170\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/44d85410fa9e0dfba57e1276d0b458ca.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=102 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/0be1b23d199d4160b34f42e83bfa65cd.poster.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/0be1b23d199d4160b34f42e83bfa65cd.webm?t=1654861170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/0be1b23d199d4160b34f42e83bfa65cd.mp4?t=1654861170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/[BRA]_STEAM_gif_Local_co-op_616x206-px.gif?t=1654861170\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/e2ab38130683f217ba1dfb2238c2e45b.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br>Enjoy new features and a major visual overhaul as you boost your high score even higher. Become a pro in no time with a brand new prologue to the game. The re-balanced difficulty makes shooting aliens even more fun for both new and experienced players.<br><br>Can you make it through endless hordes of brain-eating aliens? We mean, like, with your brain intact and everything. Prove it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/e866f28cb2b8bd47d55b69764b3bd525.poster.avif?t=1654861170\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/e866f28cb2b8bd47d55b69764b3bd525.webm?t=1654861170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342620/extras/e866f28cb2b8bd47d55b69764b3bd525.mp4?t=1654861170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
